2.Articles 18 and 19 were amended and promulgated as per the presidential order on December 28, 1948.
3.The entire act was amended and promulgated as per the presidential order on May 27, 1985.
4.Articles 6, 27-29, and 36 were amended and promulgated as per the Presidential Order of (81)-Hua-Zong-(Yi)-Yi-Zi No. 2154 on April 27, 1992.
5.Articles 3, 6, 15, and 41 were amended and promulgated as per the Presidential Order of (89)-Hua-Zong-Yi-Yi-Zi No. 8900177670 on July 19, 2000.
6.Articles 10, 28, and 32 were amended and promulgated and Articles 13-1, 39-1, and 44-1 added as per the Presidential Order of Hua-Zong-Yi-Yi-Zi No. 09100119150 on June 12, 2002.
